95
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,720
Now that's the right decision.

96
00:06:37,820 --> 00:06:38,580
Come on.

97
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,920
I know your answer now.

98
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:17,840
Hello.

99
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,160
